{"tid":1273363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位出去露營人士 請帶備以下露營物資","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T14:30:18.000Z","uid":18577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a03c53977a3660f0ae36acef20049ed9a9dcca5","tid":1273363,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"今日天朗氣清 最岩就係去露營<br />\n如果你打算出去露營<br />\n請帶備以下物品<br />\n<br />\n1.乾糧..唔好餓親<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9jL4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9jL4c.png&h=d705ba7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUU0vvY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUU0vvY.png&h=daa68123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 寶礦力..葡萄適<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioWY1CN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioWY1CN.png&h=340295fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 電筒..山路入夜會好黑..一定要帶定電筒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90gihbm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90gihbm.png&h=a6c29feb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbbeac4fa299eb4a2d3038527c0b68392d907f6d","tid":1273363,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"重有替換衣物"},{"pid":"d977a6370c258030eaac46824eaefff45ac8fbd6","tid":1273363,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"祝各下露營愉快"},{"pid":"086c2a2f0778989f54f1aadabad909e893bd9c2e","tid":1273363,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a31b83160dca11a27b0a11668c95d4ca5c50d83","tid":1273363,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedda2